<span class="header1">Arts/Communications paired with Technology (BF)</span>

<p>With a "BF" interest, you will be a valuable employee in a rapidly changing technology field. Almost all technology is in one way or another concerned with communication of change. You enjoy the mechanics of technology and you can use it to express your thoughts and feelings. The technical changes in the technology field offers a fast paced, visual, interchange of ideas and knowledge.</p>
<p>Many of the occupations in this pairing require some sort of specialized and/or technical training after high school. Many require college degrees or college level courses.</p>

